  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7532803/" class="title-link">火线上的美国梦</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7532803"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/91537188/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u91537188-7.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/91537188/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">象庭</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2015-07-14"
      class="main-meta">2015-07-14 17:44:53</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7532803_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  经常能在无数的好莱坞电影上看到英雄无畏的美国大兵单枪匹马拯救世界，也经常能在新闻报道中看到很多诸如枪杀伊拉克、阿富汗平民的丑闻，但对于美国兵的具体情形，除了这些浮光掠影的一些印象，实在是所知有限。很可喜的是，这本书则是一本很好的美国大兵普及读物，它向我们全...

